  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_parish">Parish</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_geographic_area">GEOGRAPHIC AREA</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_parish">Parishes</xref>
 are subdivisions of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authorities</xref>
 in many parts of England, with their councils being the most local level of government.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_parish">Parishes</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_office_for_national_statistics">Office for National Statistics</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.ons.gov.uk/census/2001censusandearlier/glossary/ou" scope="external" format="html">Glossary</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
